data.title: Banquet welcoming Japanese Prime Minister Eisaku Sato
data.meta_description: Prime Minister Eisaku Sato of Japan (third from left) seated next to Mayor Richard J. Daley at a banquet held in Sato\'s honor. An unidentified person (perhaps an interpreter) sits behind and between the two men. Eleanor "Sis" Daley is at the right.
